{"tid":62170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（過唔到2017）Kinder出奇蛋發明者逝世","createTime":"2016-12-31T17:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T05:23:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b2230ca960020edebb762b9a2ef9431a31b6e0","tid":62170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2016/12/31</span><br />\n 上一頁下一頁 <br />\n【明報專訊】構思出Kinder（健達）出奇蛋的意大利人薩利切（William Salice），周四在意大利帕維亞（Pavia）的醫院離世，享年83歲。他創立的基金會發聲明表示，他因中風而入院多時。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n薩利切在1960年加入意大利費列羅集團（Ferrero Rocher）後，成為朱古力大亨費列羅的得力助手。後來他為構思善用復活節朱古力的模組，發明出內裏中空、可放入玩具的Kinder出奇蛋，過去逾40年來該公司已售出數以十億枚出奇蛋。薩利切在2007年退休。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161231/s00014/1483120681631#sthash.kamFB3uL.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161231%2Fs00014%2F1483120681631%23sthash.kamFB3uL.dpuf&d=vH%2Fe%2F8PAFxDv0FWYbWPZWUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f4383765\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161231%2Fs00014%2F1483120681631%23sthash.kamFB3uL.dpuf&h=5d30339c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161231/s00014/1483120681631#sthash.kamFB3uL.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"7c7c96df71ab10a958b0ea2439b80dca7ae3f6b5","tid":62170,"uid":7080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:08:45.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f94620b205d8af2f0e33c26f4cae20ab4286d5","tid":62170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15374c618e2fd6fa67d340e6e904163427a81a52","tid":62170,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi